  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tā fakka tas leelajs Keh-\nnisch/ tas Kungē wiſſas Sem-\nnes: Redsi/ iſeij tu manna\nBreckſchā/ un neimn lihds ar te-\nvin drohſchus un fitprus Wilh-\nuß/ ſimts un divideſimte tubk-\ntoschus Rahjineekus/ un divi-\npadeſmits tubkſtoschus Sirgus\nar ſaweem Jahtneekem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un iſeij prett wiſſu to\nSemni prett Wakara Puſſi/\ntapehz ka tee mannas Muttes\nWahrdam ne irr flauntiſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un peefakki teem/ lai tee\nman gattawu turr Semni un\nUhdent/ jo es iſeeschu eeffch man-\nnas Duſmibas prett winneem/\nun apklahſchu wiſſu Senmes\nWirju ar manna Karra-Speh-\nka Rahjahm/ un dohchu tohs\nwinneem par Laupſchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta ka winnu Eewainotee\npeepldihs winnu. Celeijas un\nStrautus/ un ta Uppe usplub-\ndihs/ un taps ar winnu Mitro-\npeein pildita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es aiſweddichu winnu\nJeetinatus lihds wiſſas Semnes\nGalleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu tad iſeij/ un ueenumm\npapreekich wiſſas winnu Robbe-\nſchas/ un kad tee tew vadohjees/\ntad glabba man tohs lihds tai\nDeenat/ ka es tohs fohtiſchn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tohs/ kas neklaustigi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo tik teeschain ka ee dih-\nwoju/ un man tawa Walſitbas\nWarra trr/ ko es efimu runnaje/\nto padarrſchu es arridsan ar\nmannu Rohku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu tad ne vahrkabb ne\nweenu no teem Wahrdeem tawa\nKunga/ bet padarrt tikſufchi/ ko\neś tew efimu paweblejs/ un ue\nfawejees to paſchu darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad iſgahje Olowernis\nno fawa Kunga Watga/ un at-\naizinaja wiſſus Warrenus / un\nAhwerſtus un Wirſneekus ta\nAffirezu Karra-Spehka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un eeskaitija tohs ielaſti-\ntus Karra-Wibrus/ itt ka win-\nna Kungs tati bij pawebleje/\nſimts un divideſimte tubkſto-\nſchus/ un divipadeſmits tubk-\nſtoschus Jahtneekus/ kas Biſfe-\nnecki bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſsch taffija tohs/\nitt ka mehds tahdus Karra-Pul-\nkus taiſht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſsch nehme Kamce-\nfus un Ehſekus teem var Traf-\ntu/ fohti dauds/ir zittas Wai-\njadsibas pehz Awis un Wehr-\nſchus un Kasas ne-ieskaitama\nPulkā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Zetta-Barribu leelu\nPulku preeſch itkura Wibra/\nir Selta un Sudrabano ta keh-\nnina Namuna tohti daufs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta gabje wiſsch ar wiſſit\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
